Text: ISDA Master between MSCS and Enron Nth America Cc Sara I now attach a draft schedule to an ISDA Master Agreement between Morgan Stanley Capital Services Inc and Enron North America Corp I would be grateful if you could review the revised draft and revert with any comments that you may have I will also be forwarding you a draft Credit Support Annex for your review in due course I would be grateful if you could acknowledge receipt of this email and confirm that you are the appropriate contact at Enron North America to negotiate this ISDA Do not hesitate to contact me with any queries that you may have Regards Matthew Flett
